The Blue Devils barely resemble the team that lost five consecutive games from mid-December into January.
Pace and spaceTo any offensive structure, spacing and screening is key, and that applies to the Blue Devils' various sets.
With their two primary playmakers seemingly knowing where the other will be at all times, the Blue Devils are playing efficient and unselfish basketball.
This pleases a coaching staff that is always emphasizing team basketball and connectivity.
If they can keep this execution up, the Blue Devils could make a run in the ACC tournament and do some damage come NCAA tournament.